\zoli1 \bd Mawimbi ya \bd*\bd Wokovu\bd*\bd  yanatujia sasa. E’ Mungu, tunaomba: Ujaze sisi sote! Watakatifu wako watakasike sana! Tuimbe haleluya! Tumshukuru \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd ! \bd*
